data.description: Well loved 2 story townhome with an updated kitchen open to the living and dining areas. Luxury vinyl floors throughout, new hurricane proof front door and updated washer/dryer/refrigerator/ceiling fans. Private screened in patio and small fenced courtyard. Extra storage inside and small storage shed outside. Enjoy the community Pool and local park. This unit is close to everything Jupiter has to offer!
